HAL is a Hardware Abstraction Layer library that provides a simple unified
interface to common functionality.  The code contains:

HAL          -- Contains devices and associated device drivers like cameras,
                IMUs, GPS, etc.
PbMsgs       -- Standard messages used by sensors, loggers, etc.
Applications -- Tools for logging and reading logs.


Feel free to report any bugs or issues at our GitHub portal. You can find us at:
http://github.com/arpg/

